m_DisplayNameText.LocalisedValue: Vicious Elder Shocking Burst Light Pick +5

m_DescriptionText.LocalisedValue: This +4 agile light pick grants the wielder a +5 competence {g|Encyclopedia:Bonus}bonus{/g} on all {g|Encyclopedia:Athletics}Athletics{/g} {g|Encyclopedia:Skills}skill checks{/g}.
Whenever the wielder of this +3 keen light pick {g|Encyclopedia:Attack}attacks{/g} any enemy with {g|Encyclopedia:Damage_Reduction}DR{/g}, the DR is decreased by 1 until the end of the combat.

Whenever the wielder of this +4 ultrasound light pick lands a hit on a new enemy for the first time, the enemy must pass a {g|Encyclopedia:Saving_Throw}Fortitude saving throw{/g} ({g|Encyclopedia:DC}DC{/g} 30) or suffer {g|Encyclopedia:Damage}damage{/g} equal to its {g|Encyclopedia:Armor_Class}AC{/g}.
This is a +1 cold iron ghost touch weapon.

This is a +3 brilliant energy heartseeker weapon. This weapon can tear the soul of a living enemy: whenever it lands a hit, it deals additional {g|Encyclopedia:Dice}1d6{/g} force {g|Encyclopedia:Damage}damage{/g}.

m_FlavorText.LocalisedValue: This weapon was once the seat of Finnean's soul. Now that the soul of the Sarkorian Pathfinder has left the weapon, it has fallen silent forever.
